Primary Purpose
· Responsible for the implementation and integration of security solution(s) into customer’s environment
· Perform operation and maintenance tasks for managed environments

Responsibilities
· Responsible for implementation of network/system security (hardware and software), enforcing security policies and complying with customer requirements such as security policy and regulation.
· Performing analysis of security needs and contributes to design, integration, and installation of the relevant solution(s).
· Analysing, troubleshooting and correcting solution or product problems remotely and on-site.
· Performing operational routine such as system health check and change request
· Performing update or upgrade tasks for managed environments’ security solution(s)

